      "text": "JSON format bcs its universal\n\nServer level:\n    listen\nserver_name\nroot\nindex\nerror_page\nclient_max_body_size\n\nLocation level:\nlocation\nroot\nindex\nallow_methods\nautoindex\nreutrn\ncgi_pass\nupload_path\n\nalias\ncgi_extension",
